{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1702-02a_153","head":{"value":"[Sonnet]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", février 1702 [première partie] [tome 2], p. 153-155.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"J’ajoute un Sonnet qui a esté fait pour exciter un jeune Avocat à vaincre une certaine timidité qui l’empêche de paroître souvent au Barreau quoy qu’il ait beaucoup de talent &amp; de grandes parties pour y acquerir de la gloire.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"value":"SONNET.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label"}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quelle raison, dis-moy, quelle necessité","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Peut t’imposer le joug d’un austere silence ?","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Manques tu de sçavoir, de feu, de vehemence ;","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Répons, est-ce prudence, est-ce timidité ?","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des yeux de nos Argus ne crains point la clarté,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par la sublime voix de ta vive éloquence","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tonne dans le barreau, fais taire l’ignorance,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et contre le mensonge arme la verité.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Terrasse la chicane &amp; confons l’injustice,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce beau champ est ouvert, va, cours dans cette lice,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’un visage assuré, d’un pas ferme &amp; certain.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Montre toy de nos loix un fidelle interprete,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et des droits de Thémis un vigoureux Athlete","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un digne éleve enfin de l’Orateur Romain.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}}]}}]}}}